snippet.title: Insider trailer1
snippet.description:
INSIDERS is a single-player adventure game set inside of human body. 
-Huge open word full of danger. 
-Pilot the ship
-Mine resources
-Build bases
-Craft items and weapons
-Fight enemies

release on steam 2021.4
